short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Easily import bulk products from AliExpress to your online store. Automatically fulfill your orders on AliExpress by one click.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The extension is a part of Prestashop Dropshipping Aliexpress Module..
So when use the extension, you must download Prestashop Dropshipping Aliexpress module:  https://addons.prestashop.com/en/45060-dropshipping-aliexpress.html

The extension will do the tasks:
- Load product data from Aliexpress.com and send to Prestashop module.
- Automatic placed your order in Aliexpress.
